[[File:SpittingRawlTK.png|thumb|A poster showing the Spitting Rawl Technique]]
The '''Spitting Rawl Technique''' was a [[Teräs Käsi/Legends|Teräs Käsi]] attack named after the [[Species/Legends|creature]] of the [[Fanned rawl|same name]]. It was portrayed in the ''[[Spitting Rawl]]'' [[Painting/Legends|poster]].<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
The Spitting Rawl Technique was portrayed in the ''Spitting Rawl'' painting in the [[2003]] [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online roleplaying game]] [[Star Wars Galaxies|''Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided'']], prior to the [[Star Wars video games|game's]] closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="SWG" /><ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref>

